thread.title: Cleveland will tie, could break record number of consecutive days above 50 degrees in February

author: Kelly Reardon, cleveland.com
title: Cleveland will tie, could break record number of consecutive days above 50 degrees in February
text: This Friday, Cleveland will tie the record number of consecutive days with temperatures above 50 degrees in February.
